      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a parts car or a major restoration project. The engine requires significant work to be reliably roadworthy, and there are noticeable mechanical issues including a failing suspension and exhaust leaks. The exterior shows heavy wear with significant rust patches, peeling clear coat, and several dents, while the interior has torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is priced to reflect these extensive needs and is sold strictly as-is.",
