    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s still in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
